Quickstrike:





Quickstrike, in the forest by the Predacon base concentrated and 
mapped the coordinates Black Arachnia gave to him in his mind. It was 
true, it was a good distance away. 

"Dang, all th' way down there." he remarked. He looked at Dark 
Mouse. "Well let's head out. Ah'll lead th' way." He started off, 
going wide around the ship from out the forest.
